---
hvy_version: 0.1
title: Resume Example
component_defs:
  - name: history-record
    baseType: expandable
    description: Expandable resume history record
    schema:
      component: history-record
      css: "margin: 0.35rem 0;"
      expandableAlwaysShowStub: true
      expandableExpanded: false
      expandableStubBlocks:
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: table
            css: "margin: 0;"
            tableColumns: "YEAR, ORGANIZATION, TITLE"
            tableShowHeader: false
            tableRows:
              - cells:
                  - "2024"
                  - "Northwind Labs"
                  - "Senior Software Engineer"
      expandableContentBlocks:
        - text: "### Senior Software Engineer"
          schema:
            component: text
            css: "margin: 0 0 0.35rem;"
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: grid
            css: "margin: 0.35rem 0;"
            gridColumns: 2
            gridItems:
              - id: history-location
                column: left
                block:
                  text: "Seattle, WA"
                  schema:
                    component: text
                    css: "margin: 0;"
              - id: history-date-range
                column: right
                block:
                  text: "05/2024 - present"
                  schema:
                    component: text
                    css: "margin: 0; text-align: right;"
        - text: "Platform and AI Infrastructure Lead"
          schema:
            component: text
            css: "margin: 0.35rem 0; font-weight: 700;"
        - text: "Led the developer platform for an AI-enabled product line, improving local setup, internal tooling, and release confidence across a fast-moving engineering team."
          schema:
            component: text
            css: "margin: 0.35rem 0;"
        - text: "#### Accomplishments"
          schema:
            component: text
            css: "margin: 0.6rem 0 0.25rem;"
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: component-list
            componentListComponent: text
            css: "margin: 0;"
            componentListBlocks:
              - text: "Built a shared TypeScript platform package that reduced duplicated application code across three products."
                schema:
                  component: text
                  css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
              - text: "Introduced reproducible developer containers and test workflows that cut onboarding time from days to hours."
                schema:
                  component: text
                  css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
              - text: "Partnered with design and product to ship AI-assisted editor workflows with measurable adoption."
                schema:
                  component: text
                  css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: skills-and-tools-tech-list
            css: "margin: 0.6rem 0 0;"
            gridColumns: 2
            gridItems:
              - id: history-skills
                column: left
                block:
                  text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: component-list
                    componentListComponent: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0;"
                    align: center
                    componentListBlocks:
                      - text: "#### Relevant Skills"
                        schema:
                          component: text
                          css: "margin: 0 0 0.25rem;"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "Software Engineering"
                          xrefTarget: "skill-software-engineering"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "Library Development"
                          xrefTarget: "skill-library-development"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "Project Management"
                          xrefTarget: "skill-project-management"
              - id: history-tools-technologies
                column: right
                block:
                  text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: component-list
                    componentListComponent: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0;"
                    align: center
                    componentListBlocks:
                      - text: "#### Tools and Technologies"
                        schema:
                          component: text
                          css: "margin: 0 0 0.25rem;"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "TypeScript"
                          xrefTarget: "tool-typescript"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "Python"
                          xrefTarget: "tool-python"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "Developer Containers"
                          xrefTarget: "tool-developer-containers"
  - name: skills-and-tools-tech-list
    baseType: grid
    description: Two-column skills and tools list using xref-cards
    schema:
      component: skills-and-tools-tech-list
      css: "margin: 0.6rem 0 0;"
      gridColumns: 2
      gridItems:
        - id: relevant-skills
          column: left
          block:
            text: ""
            schema:
              component: component-list
              componentListComponent: xref-card
              css: "margin: 0;"
              align: center
              componentListBlocks:
                - text: "#### Relevant Skills"
                  schema:
                    component: text
                    css: "margin: 0 0 0.25rem;"
                - text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                    xrefTitle: "Software Engineering"
                    xrefTarget: "skill-software-engineering"
                - text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                    xrefTitle: "Library Development"
                    xrefTarget: "skill-library-development"
                - text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                    xrefTitle: "LLM Prompt Engineering"
                    xrefTarget: "skill-llm-prompt-engineering"
        - id: tools-technologies
          column: right
          block:
            text: ""
            schema:
              component: component-list
              componentListComponent: xref-card
              css: "margin: 0;"
              align: center
              componentListBlocks:
                - text: "#### Tools and Technologies"
                  schema:
                    component: text
                    css: "margin: 0 0 0.25rem;"
                - text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                    xrefTitle: "TypeScript"
                    xrefTarget: "tool-typescript"
                - text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                    xrefTitle: "Python"
                    xrefTarget: "tool-python"
                - text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                    xrefTitle: "Developer Containers"
                    xrefTarget: "tool-developer-containers"
  - name: education-record
    baseType: expandable
    description: Expandable education record
    schema:
      component: education-record
      css: "margin: 0.35rem 0;"
      expandableAlwaysShowStub: true
      expandableExpanded: false
      expandableStubBlocks:
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: table
            css: "margin: 0;"
            tableColumns: "DEGREE, INSTITUTION, LOCATION"
            tableShowHeader: false
            tableRows:
              - cells:
                  - "B.S. Computer Science"
                  - "University of Washington"
                  - "Seattle, WA"
      expandableContentBlocks:
        - text: "### B.S. Computer Science"
          schema:
            component: text
            css: "margin: 0 0 0.35rem;"
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: grid
            css: "margin: 0.35rem 0;"
            gridColumns: 2
            gridItems:
              - id: education-institution-details
                column: left
                block:
                  text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: component-list
                    componentListComponent: text
                    css: "margin: 0;"
                    componentListBlocks:
                      - text: "University of Washington"
                        schema:
                          component: text
                          css: "margin: 0;"
                      - text: "Seattle, WA"
                        schema:
                          component: text
                          css: "margin: 0.15rem 0 0;"
                      - text: "GPA: 3.8 / 4.0"
                        schema:
                          component: text
                          css: "margin: 0.15rem 0 0;"
              - id: education-date-range
                column: right
                block:
                  text: "09/2019 - 06/2023"
                  schema:
                    component: text
                    css: "margin: 0; text-align: right;"
        - text: "Focused on systems programming, developer tooling, and human-computer interaction while building software for research and product-oriented team projects."
          schema:
            component: text
            css: "margin: 0.5rem 0;"
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: skills-and-tools-tech-list
            css: "margin: 0.6rem 0 0;"
            gridColumns: 2
            gridItems:
              - id: education-relevant-skills
                column: left
                block:
                  text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: component-list
                    componentListComponent: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0;"
                    align: center
                    componentListBlocks:
                      - text: "#### Relevant Skills"
                        schema:
                          component: text
                          css: "margin: 0 0 0.25rem;"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "Software Engineering"
                          xrefTarget: "skill-software-engineering"
              - id: education-tools-technologies
                column: right
                block:
                  text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: component-list
                    componentListComponent: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0;"
                    align: center
                    componentListBlocks:
                      - text: "#### Tools and Technologies"
                        schema:
                          component: text
                          css: "margin: 0 0 0.25rem;"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "Python"
                          xrefTarget: "tool-python"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "C/C++"
                          xrefTarget: "tool-c-cpp"
        - text: "#### Classes"
          schema:
            component: text
            css: "margin: 0.6rem 0 0.25rem;"
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: component-list
            componentListComponent: text
            css: "margin: 0;"
            componentListBlocks:
              - text: "Distributed Systems"
                schema:
                  component: text
                  css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
              - text: "Operating Systems"
                schema:
                  component: text
                  css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
              - text: "Compilers"
                schema:
                  component: text
                  css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
              - text: "Machine Learning"
                schema:
                  component: text
                  css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
              - text: "Computer Graphics"
                schema:
                  component: text
                  css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
              - text: "Human-Computer Interaction"
                schema:
                  component: text
                  css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
  - name: project-record
    baseType: expandable
    description: Expandable project record
    schema:
      component: project-record
      css: "margin: 0.35rem 0;"
      expandableAlwaysShowStub: true
      expandableExpanded: false
      expandableStubBlocks:
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: table
            css: "margin: 0;"
            tableColumns: "PROJECT, DATE"
            tableShowHeader: false
            tableRows:
              - cells:
                  - "Atlas Console"
                  - "01/2024 - 04/2024"
      expandableContentBlocks:
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: grid
            css: "margin: 0 0 0.35rem;"
            gridColumns: 2
            gridItems:
              - id: project-title
                column: left
                block:
                  text: "### Atlas Console"
                  schema:
                    component: text
                    css: "margin: 0;"
              - id: project-date-range
                column: right
                block:
                  text: "01/2024 - 04/2024"
                  schema:
                    component: text
                    css: "margin: 0; text-align: right;"
        - text: "Built an internal observability dashboard for AI-assisted workflows, with trace inspection, failure clustering, and lightweight experiment comparisons."
          schema:
            component: text
            css: "margin: 0.5rem 0;"
        - text: "[Visit webpage](https://example.com/atlas-console) (example.com)"
          schema:
            component: text
            css: "margin: 0.35rem 0;"
        - text: ""
          schema:
            component: skills-and-tools-tech-list
            css: "margin: 0.6rem 0 0;"
            gridColumns: 2
            gridItems:
              - id: project-relevant-skills
                column: left
                block:
                  text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: component-list
                    componentListComponent: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0;"
                    align: center
                    componentListBlocks:
                      - text: "#### Relevant Skills"
                        schema:
                          component: text
                          css: "margin: 0 0 0.25rem;"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "Software Engineering"
                          xrefTarget: "skill-software-engineering"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "LLM Prompt Engineering"
                          xrefTarget: "skill-llm-prompt-engineering"
              - id: project-tools-technologies
                column: right
                block:
                  text: ""
                  schema:
                    component: component-list
                    componentListComponent: xref-card
                    css: "margin: 0;"
                    align: center
                    componentListBlocks:
                      - text: "#### Tools and Technologies"
                        schema:
                          component: text
                          css: "margin: 0 0 0.25rem;"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "TypeScript"
                          xrefTarget: "tool-typescript"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "Python"
                          xrefTarget: "tool-python"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "OpenAI API"
                          xrefTarget: "tool-openai-api"
                      - text: ""
                        schema:
                          component: xref-card
                          css: "margin: 0.25rem 0;"
                          xrefTitle: "Developer Containers"
                          xrefTarget: "tool-developer-containers"
---

<!--hvy: {"id":"header","lock":true}-->
#! Info

<!--hvy:text {"css":"margin-bottom: 0;","align":"center"}-->
# Avery Hart

<!--hvy:text {"css":"margin-top: 0;","align":"center"}-->
[AY-vuh-ree HART]

<!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0.5rem 0; margin-top: 1rem;","align":"center"}-->
Senior Software Engineer

<!--hvy: {"id":"summary","lock":true}-->
#! Summary

<!--hvy:expandable {"css":"margin: 0.5rem 0;","expandableAlwaysShowStub":true,"expandableExpanded":false,"lock":true}-->

<!--hvy:expandable:0 {"component":"text","css":"margin-bottom: 0;","lock":true}-->
## Summary

<!--hvy:expandable:0 {"component":"text","css":"margin-top: 0;","lock":true}-->
Product-minded software engineer focused on developer tooling, AI workflows, and reusable systems that make complex products easier to ship and maintain.

<!--hvy:expandable:1 {"component":"text","css":"margin: 0;","lock":true}-->
- Builds polished internal tools that reduce friction for engineers and product teams.
- Comfortable moving between frontend UX, platform design, and AI-assisted workflows.
- Enjoys turning messy, high-context problems into repeatable systems and clear documentation.

<!--hvy: {"id":"locations","lock":true}-->
#! Locations

<!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0.5rem 0;","lock":true}-->
**Location:** Seattle, WA

<!--hvy:text {"css":"margin: 0.5rem 0;","lock":true}-->
**Target Location(s):** Remote, Seattle, San Francisco

<!--hvy: {"id":"top-skills-tools-technologies","lock":true}-->
#! Top Skills, Tools, and Technologies

<!--hvy:grid {"css":"margin: 0.5rem 0; gap: 0.75rem;","gridColumns":2,"lock":true}-->

<!--hvy:grid:0 {"id":"top-skills","column":"left","component":"component-list","componentListComponent":"xref-card","css":"margin: 0;","align":"center"}-->

