<!--hvy:expandable:1 {"component":"text","css":"margin: 0 0 0.35rem;"}-->
### Senior Software Engineer

<!--hvy:expandable:1 {"component":"grid","css":"margin: 0.35rem 0;","gridColumns":2}-->

<!--hvy:grid:0 {"id":"history-location","column":"left","component":"text","css":"margin: 0;"}-->
Seattle, WA

<!--hvy:grid:1 {"id":"history-date-range","column":"right","component":"text","css":"margin: 0; text-align: right;"}-->
05/2024 - present

<!--hvy:expandable:1 {"component":"text","css":"margin: 0.35rem 0; font-weight: 700;"}-->
Platform and AI Infrastructure Lead

<!--hvy:expandable:1 {"component":"text","css":"margin: 0.35rem 0;"}-->
Led the developer platform for an AI-enabled product line, improving local setup, internal tooling, and release confidence across a fast-moving engineering team.

<!--hvy:expandable:1 {"component":"text","css":"margin: 0.6rem 0 0.25rem;"}-->
#### Accomplishments

<!--hvy:expandable:1 {"component":"component-list","componentListComponent":"text","css":"margin: 0;"}-->

<!--hvy:component-list:0 {"component":"text","css":"margin: 0.25rem 0;"}-->
Built a shared TypeScript platform package that reduced duplicated application code across three products.

<!--hvy:component-list:1 {"component":"text","css":"margin: 0.25rem 0;"}-->
Introduced reproducible developer containers and test workflows that cut onboarding time from days to hours.

<!--hvy:component-list:2 {"component":"text","css":"margin: 0.25rem 0;"}-->
Partnered with design and product to ship AI-assisted editor workflows with measurable adoption.

