<!--hvy:expandable:0 {"component":"table","css":"margin: 0;","tableColumns":"PROJECT, DATE","tableShowHeader":false,"tableRows":[{"cells":["Heavy Stack","05/2024 - present"]}]}-->

<!--hvy:expandable:1 {"component":"grid","css":"margin: 0 0 0.35rem;","gridColumns":2}-->

<!--hvy:grid:0 {"id":"project-title","column":"left","component":"text","css":"margin: 0;"}-->
### Heavy Stack

<!--hvy:grid:1 {"id":"project-date-range","column":"right","component":"text","css":"margin: 0; text-align: right;"}-->
05/2024 - present

<!--hvy:expandable:1 {"component":"text","css":"margin: 0.5rem 0;"}-->
The Heavy Stack is the production version of the developer container used for Heavy Resume. It has various features such as hot reloading for both the application and testing, the ability to record user actions for playback later, as well as a functioning dev container with databases and everything set up and ready to go.

<!--hvy:expandable:1 {"component":"text","css":"margin: 0.35rem 0;"}-->
[Visit webpage](https://github.com) (github.com)

